snippet.title: Frankenstein's Monster for the Atari 2600
snippet.description:
One of THE best Atari 2600 games EVER!

It is like Pitfall! but more challenging and without the sidescrolling.

It also features THE best Atari 2600 game over screen (which you can see in this video)
